# This file is created automatically during installation

The installer (.dev-aid/scripts/install.sh) will create symlinks like:
- CLAUDE.md (if Claude is enabled)
- GEMINI.md (if Gemini is enabled)  
- OPENAI.md (if OpenAI is enabled)

These symlinks point to .dev-aid/providers/{provider}/{PROVIDER}.md

You don't need to create these manually.
